'''Tutlayt''' (Asget: '''Tutlayin''') d asizeɣ n [[azmul|yizmal]] akk d [[azamul|izamulen]] id yesnulfayen afecku gar n ifecka n [[tamusni|tmusni]], Tutlayt d allal n umsegzi d wemray ilan (isɛan) yakk azal ameqran sɣur [[afgan|ifganen]] n tmetti deg yall anrar neɣ taɣult n tudert, Tutlayt teqqen s usrid d [[Asekti|usekti]] (axemmem), Acku tikta n ufgan ttefɣent-d seg yiles n ufgan 
Imusnawen snetmen-d d akken llan-t gar n 5000 ar 7000 n tutlayin deg umadal

== Aẓaṛ == 
Megaraden-t tiẓra n uẓar n tutlayin 

